### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ServerSync Integration Tests
### Protocol: attestation-based differential sync
### Endpoints:
###   GET    /sync/attestations  → SyncAggregateAttestation
###   POST   /sync               → SyncAggregateResponse (download)
###   PATCH  /sync               → SyncUploadResponse (upload upsert)
###   DELETE /sync               → SyncDeleteResponse
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###
### NOTE: Polymorphic sealed classes use a "type" discriminator. The format
### below assumes default kotlinx.serialization CLASS_NAME mode with "."
### separator for nested classes. If the server returns 400, verify the
### exact discriminator by examining the server's Json configuration in
### synapse/core/.../statics/Serialization.kt

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. GET Attestations (baseline: fingerprint→checksum mappings)
###    Returns SyncAggregateAttestation { entries: [{fingerprint, checksum, scope}] }
###    Empty list if no sync data for user's scopes
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{server}}/sync/attestations
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Accept: application/json

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. PATCH Upload (New NotePacket)
###    Creates a new sync entry. Server assigns UUID fingerprint.
###    Returns SyncUploadResponse { accepted: {key → SyncEntryFull}, rejected: {key → RejectionReason} }
###    Save the returned fingerprint from accepted["upload-1"].fingerprint for subsequent tests
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "upload-1": {
    "type": "cloud.mallne.dicentra.areaassist.model.sync.SyncUpsert.New",
    "packet": {
      "type": "cloud.mallne.dicentra.areaassist.model.sync.SyncPacket.NotePacket",
      "link": {
        "forParcel": "sync-integration-test-parcel",
        "serviceHint": "sync-test"
      },
      "note": "Integration test: verify upload flow"
    },
    "scope": "user:mallne"
  },
  "upload-2": {
    "type": "cloud.mallne.dicentra.areaassist.model.sync.SyncUpsert.New",
    "packet": {
      "type": "cloud.mallne.dicentra.areaassist.model.sync.SyncPacket.NotePacket",
      "link": {
        "forParcel": "sync-integration-test-parcel",
        "serviceHint": "sync-test"
      },
      "note": "Integration test: second entry for batch download test"
    },
    "scope": "user:mallne"
  }
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. GET Attestations (verify entries exist after upload)
###    Should now show 2 entries matching the NotePackets above.
###    Note the fingerprint values returned.
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{server}}/sync/attestations
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Accept: application/json

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 4. POST Download (all entries for user's scopes)
###    Body: null → downloads ALL entries for the authenticated user's scopes.
###    Returns SyncAggregateResponse { entries: [SyncEntryFull, ...], timestamp }
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

null

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 5. POST Download (filtered by fingerprints)
###    REPLACE the fingerprint values below with actual values from step 3.
###    Returns only the requested entries (or empty for unknown fingerprints)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

[
  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
]

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 6. PATCH Upload (Update existing entry)
###    REPLACE fingerprint with a real value from step 3.
###    Server increments version, updates checksum, sets blame.
###    Returns SyncUploadResponse with updated SyncEntryFull.
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "update-1": {
    "type": "cloud.mallne.dicentra.areaassist.model.sync.SyncUpsert.Update",
    "fingerprint": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "packet": {
      "type": "cloud.mallne.dicentra.areaassist.model.sync.SyncPacket.NotePacket",
      "link": {
        "forParcel": "sync-integration-test-parcel",
        "serviceHint": "sync-test"
      },
      "note": "Integration test: verify update flow - content modified"
    },
    "scope": "user:mallne"
  }
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. DELETE entries by fingerprint
###    REPLACE fingerprints with real values from step 3.
###    Returns SyncDeleteResponse { accepted: [...], rejected: [...], timestamp }
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

[
  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
]

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8. GET Attestations (verify deletion)
###    Should now return empty list if both entries were deleted.
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{server}}/sync/attestations
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Accept: application/json

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 9. DELETE unknown fingerprints (verify error handling)
###    Unknown fingerprints are silently accepted (no matching entry to protect).
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

[
  "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000009999"
]

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 10. POST Download with empty fingerprint list
###     Empty list returns empty response (no entries match nothing).
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{server}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("keycloak")}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

[]

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 11. Unauthenticated request (verify 401)
###     All sync endpoints require authentication.
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{server}}/sync/attestations